'''約翰·理察·朗尼'''（{{lang-en|'''John Richard Rooney'''}}，{{bd|1990年|12月17日|catidx=Rooney, John}}）出生於[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[默西賽德郡|默西賽德郡]][[利物浦|利物浦]]，具有[[爱尔兰人|爱尔兰人]]血統，是一名[[英式足球|足球]][[運動員|運動員]]，司職[[前鋒_(足球)|前鋒]]，現時效力[[英格蘭足球全國聯賽_(第一級)|英格蘭足球全國聯賽]]球會[[斯托克港足球俱乐部|史托港]]。

約翰是[[德比郡足球俱乐部|德比郡足球俱乐部]]教練[[韦恩·鲁尼|韦恩·鲁尼]]的弟弟。

==生平==
===球會===
約翰·朗尼與他的兄弟們一同於[[埃弗顿足球俱乐部|愛華頓]]青訓系統受訓，惟於14歲時被棄用。他於2007年加盟[[英乙|英乙]]球會[[马科斯菲尔德足球俱乐部|馬爾斯菲]]的足球學院，當時約翰仍就讀其中學最後的一年，球隊與其學校取得協議，讓他週一與週二隨青年隊訓練，週三傍晚參加足球學院，而週日則為U-16青年隊上陣<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.manchestereveningnews.co.uk/sport/football/macclesfield_town/s/525/525854_macc_sign_rooney.html |title=Macc sign Rooney |publisher=manchestereveningnews.co.uk |date=2007-03-07 |accessdate=2009-12-22}}</ref></small>。同年暑假表現出色的約翰獲提供兩年獎學金。

約翰於2008年3月24日主場對[[巴尼特足球俱乐部|班列特]]於完場前首次後補為一隊上陣<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/7298302.stm |title=Macclesfield 3-0 Barnet |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-03-24 |accessdate=2009-12-22 |archive-date=2020-11-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201113084912/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/7298302.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>；季末對[[切斯特城足球俱乐部|車士打]]更首次獲派正選上陣<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/7368629.stm |title=Chester 0-0 Macclesfield |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-05-03 |accessdate=2009-12-22 |archive-date=2019-08-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190830133258/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/7368629.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。7月14日約翰簽署為期兩年的首份[[職業|職業]]合約<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/macclesfield_town/7505233.stm |title=Rooney signs Macclesfield deal |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-07-14 |accessdate=2009-12-22 |archive-date=2020-11-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125092657/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/macclesfield_town/7505233.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

在[[2008年至2009年英格蘭足球乙級聯賽|2008/09年球季]]獲得數場後補上陣機會後，於2009年3月14日主場迎戰[[伯恩茅斯足球俱乐部|般尼茅夫]]再次正選上陣<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/7923360.stm |title=Macclesfield 0-2 Bournemouth |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-03-14 |accessdate=2009-12-22 |archive-date=2019-08-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190827141927/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/7923360.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>；兩週後作客[[达根汉姆和雷德布里奇足球俱乐部|杜根咸]]射入個人首個入球<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/7948991.stm |title=Dag & Red 2-1 Macclesfield |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-03-28 |accessdate=2009-12-22 |archive-date=2019-09-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190901151428/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/7948991.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>；4月11日作客[[切斯特城足球俱乐部|車士打]]，約翰再下一城，於離門20[[碼|碼]]「窩利」射入先拔頭籌<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/7979651.stm |title=Chester 0-2 Macclesfield |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-04-11 |accessdate=2009-12-22 |archive-date=2019-09-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190903065115/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/7979651.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。首個正式球季在聯賽上陣14場，其中10場擔任正選，射入兩球。

約翰的表現吸引一眾[[英超|英超]]球會的注目<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_5515070,00.html |title=Alexander fears Rooney exit |publisher=sKY SportS |date=2009-08-26 |accessdate=2009-12-22 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310081025/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_5515070,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，但[[2009年至2010年英格蘭足球乙級聯賽|2009/10年球季]]他的腳風不順，直到2009年10月6日[[英格蘭聯賽錦標|英格蘭聯賽錦標]]2-4負於[[卡莱尔联足球俱乐部|卡素爾]]才射入首球<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/8284788.stm |title=Carlisle 4-2 Macclesfield |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-10-06 |accessdate=2009-12-22 |archive-date=2020-05-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200503031636/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/8284788.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>；10天後作客[[切尔滕汉姆足球俱乐部|車頓咸]]才打破本季9場聯賽的入球荒<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/8295392.stm |title=Cheltenham 1-2 Macclesfield |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-10-16 |accessdate=2009-12-12 |archive-date=2009-10-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091018225156/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/8295392.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。2010年2月約翰獲邀到[[英冠|英冠]]球會[[德比郡足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:德比郡;zh-hk:打比郡}-]]試訓1週，並參與預備隊對[[谢菲尔德联足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:谢菲尔德联;zh-hk:錫菲聯}-]]的賽事<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11688_5971034,00.html |title=Rams take Rooney on trial |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2010-02-22 |accessdate=2010-02-23 |archive-date=2016-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309144759/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11688_5971034,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，但賽事因大雪取消，打比郡領隊[[尼祖·哥洛夫|尼祖·哥洛夫]]表示對約翰操練表現滿意，仍需觀察實戰表現才決定來季會否提供合約<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/d/derby_county/8537084.stm |title=Derby County ponder deal for Macclesfield's John Rooney |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-02-25 |accessdate=2010-02-26 |archive-date=2019-08-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190831175038/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/d/derby_county/8537084.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。約翰於3月3日代表打比郡預備隊上陣對[[谢周三足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:谢周三;zh-hk:錫周三}-]]，踢足全場90分鐘，賽後返回馬爾斯菲<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/d/derby_county/8549180.stm |title=John Rooney turns out for Derby County reserves |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-03-04 |accessdate=2010-03-06 |archive-date=2019-08-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190829092536/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/d/derby_county/8549180.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

最終尼祖·哥洛夫決定放棄約翰，兩季以來僅為馬爾斯菲射入4球，雖然球隊仍然提供新合約，但他在季後在一支[[英甲|英甲]]球隊跟操而沒有續約<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/macclesfield_town/8802154.stm |title=John Rooney yet to sign new Macclesfield Town contract |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-07-08 |accessdate=2010-07-09 |archive-date=2019-08-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190829092534/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/macclesfield_town/8802154.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

季前約翰跟隨[[哈德斯菲尔德足球俱乐部|哈德斯菲爾德]]試訓，但無法贏得一紙合約<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11719_6269567,00.html |title=Terriers opt against Rooney |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2010-07-19 |accessdate=2011-03-23 |archive-date=2013-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131224111557/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11719_6269567,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他其後轉赴[[美國|美國]]參加不同球隊的試訓，並與[[美國職業足球大聯盟|美國職業足球大聯盟]]簽約參加2011年「美職聯超級選秀會」（MLS SuperDraft），於第二輪第25選獲[[紐約紅牛|紐約紅牛]]相中<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.nj.com/redbulls/index.ssf/2011/01/red_bulls_draft_pick_john_rooney_looking_to_make_name_for_himself.html |title=Red Bulls draft pick John Rooney looking to make name for himself |publisher=''nj.com'' |date=2011-01-14 |accessdate=2011-03-23 |archive-date=2012-11-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121103183642/http://www.nj.com/redbulls/index.ssf/2011/01/red_bulls_draft_pick_john_rooney_looking_to_make_name_for_himself.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2012年10月25日，約翰·朗尼加盟[[英冠|英冠]][[巴恩斯利足球俱乐部|班士利]]，合約至2013年夏季<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/20089064 |title=Wayne Rooney's brother John joins Barnsley |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2012-10-25 |accessdate=2013-10-06 |archive-date=2012-12-10 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6CoXMSWLR?url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/20089064 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。但加盟後從未為球會正式上場，至2013年5月9日，[[巴恩斯利足球俱乐部|班士利]]宣佈放棄約翰·朗尼<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-2321828/John-Rooney-younger-brother-Wayne-released-Barnsley.html |title=Rooney released! Wayne's younger brother John axed by Barnsley after failing to play a single game for Championship strugglers |publisher=''Daily Mail'' |date=2013-05-09 |accessdate=2013-10-06 |archive-date=2020-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111194855/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-2321828/John-Rooney-younger-brother-Wayne-released-Barnsley.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2013年7月10日，約翰·朗尼加盟[[英乙|英乙]][[貝里足球俱樂部|貝利]]，合約為期一年<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/23254815 |title=Wayne Rooney's brother John joins League Two side Bury |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2013-07-10 |accessdate=2013-10-06 |archive-date=2013-09-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130901161258/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/23254815 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===國家隊===
約翰·朗尼雖然在[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]出生，亦具有代表[[愛爾蘭國家足球隊|愛爾蘭]]參加國際賽的資格，他曾表示願意為愛爾蘭效力<small><ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://news.sky.com/skynews/Home/Sky-News-Archive/Article/20080641312932 |title=Rooney's Brother Set To Play For Ireland |publisher=Sky News |date=2008-04-15 |accessdate=2009-12-22 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100104092345/http://news.sky.com/skynews/Home/Sky-News-Archive/Article/20080641312932 |archivedate=2010-01-04 }}</ref></small>。

==私人生活==
約翰·朗尼遷入[[韦恩·鲁尼|哥哥]]位於[[柴郡|柴郡]]切爾滕納姆（Prestbury）的居所，距離馬爾斯菲主場僅20分鐘車程，方便他日常往返。當時仍為學徒球員身份賺取週薪150[[英鎊|英鎊]]的約翰被隊友取笑，如付不起租金，只好為哥哥買[[杯麵|杯麵]]填數<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.thesun.co.uk/sol/homepage/showbiz/bizarre/article1509110.ece |title=Spare Roon for Wayne's brother |publisher=[[太陽報_(英國)|''thesun.co.uk'']] |date=2008-08-04 |accessdate=2009-12-22 |archive-date=2009-11-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091102080431/http://www.thesun.co.uk/sol/homepage/showbiz/bizarre/article1509110.ece |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

